OL,3,CSmall businesses say fees to use parks
OL,4,Cand Downs in Bristol are extortionate
OL,6,FSmall business owners in Bristol say
OL,7,Fthe introduction of charges to use
OL,8,Fparks and green spaces in the city
OL,9,Fwill have a serious impact on their
OL,10,Fincome.
OL,12,FBristol City Council say the charges
OL,13,Fof up to #800 + VAT in parks will
OL,14,Fensure companies running paidfor
OL,15,Factivities meet required standards,
OL,16,Fincluding having appropriate insurance.
OL,18,FProfessional dog walkers will be
OL,19,Frequired to pay up to #500 + VAT.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
