CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773087074
OL,3,CSmall businesses say fees to use parks
OL,4,Cand Downs in Bristol are extortionate
OL,6,FOthers facing the charges, which will
OL,7,Fbe introduced April 1 2026, include
OL,8,Foutdoor yoga teachers and instructors
OL,9,Frunning bootcamp-style sessions.
OL,10,FSmaller businesses will be offered a
OL,11,F50% discount if they are based in
OL,12,FBristol.
OL,14,FThe Downs Committee sets its own
OL,15,Fcharging structure for commercial
OL,16,Factivities on The Downs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
