PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773087074
OL,3,CSmall businesses say fees to use parks
OL,4,Cand Downs in Bristol are extortionate
OL,6,FPaid fitness classes or personal
OL,7,Ftraining sessions will require an
OL,8,Fannual Downs licence costing #900 for
OL,9,Fsessions with fewer than 19 people or
OL,10,F#2,600 for sessions with 20 or more
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,FBusinesses who run fitness classes
OL,14,Fdescribe the fees for The Downs as
OL,15,F"eye-wateringly extortionate".
OL,17,FA group of protestors gathered at the
OL,18,Fmeeting of The Downs Committee on
OL,19,FMonday afternoon.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
