OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773087074
OL,3,CSmall businesses say fees to use parks
OL,4,Cand Downs in Bristol are extortionate
OL,6,FOne said: "You're double taxing local
OL,7,Fresidents, who will ultimately have to
OL,8,Ffoot this, I know people who are going
OL,9,Fto stop operating on The Downs because
OL,10,Fof this."
OL,12,FAnother protestor added: "It feels
OL,13,Funfair, it's a community space, it's a
OL,14,Fgreat way to use it, it keeps us all
OL,15,Ffit and healthy, it keeps us out of
OL,16,Fhospitals, it's just wrong.
OL,18,F"It's a shame we've got to the stage
OL,19,Fof asking for more money from people
OL,20,Fwho are only doing good for the
OL,21,Fcommunity."
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@IO]tD@ZOUzD@AOU}D@KO]
