PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773087074
OL,3,CSmall businesses say fees to use parks
OL,4,Cand Downs in Bristol are extortionate
OL,6,FProfessional dog walker Sophie Hunter
OL,7,Ffrom Jurassic Bark has been running
OL,8,Fher business for 10 years.
OL,10,FShe currently walks six dogs twice a
OL,11,Fday. But she said she will be impacted
OL,12,Fby the four dog walking limit when it
OL,13,Fis introduced next month.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773087074
OL,3,CSmall businesses say fees to use parks
OL,4,Cand Downs in Bristol are extortionate
OL,6,FMs Hunter said: "I feel worried
OL,7,Fbecause they are essentially capping
OL,8,Four income as group dog walkers.
OL,9,FThey're saying we can only walk a
OL,10,Fmaximum of four dogs which means
OL,11,Fpotentially 33% less income. I'll have
OL,12,Fto put my prices up which could make
OL,13,Fit unaffordable for some."
OL,15,FShe admitted she is worried about her
OL,16,Fbusiness and that dog walking will
OL,17,Fbecome unaffordable if things continue
OL,18,Fthis way.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773087074
OL,3,CSmall businesses say fees to use parks
OL,4,Cand Downs in Bristol are extortionate
OL,6,FSophie said she and many other dog
OL,7,Fwalkers are professionals who can walk
OL,8,Fsix dogs safely.
OL,10,FThe council says it paused the
OL,11,Fintroduction of the scheme in 2025
OL,12,Ffollowing feedback from small
OL,13,Fbusinesses, adding a review has now
OL,14,Fbeen completed, and the revised
OL,15,Fstructure is designed to be fairer,
OL,16,Fclearer, and more reflective of the
OL,17,Fdifferent types of businesses
OL,18,Foperating across the city's green
OL,19,Fspaces.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
