OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773087074
OL,3,CSmall businesses say fees to use parks
OL,4,Cand Downs in Bristol are extortionate
OL,6,FCllr Stephen Williams, Chair of the
OL,7,FPublic Health and Communities
OL,8,FCommittee, said the scheme is about
OL,9,Fensuring public safety.
OL,11,FHe said: "This is not about raising
OL,12,Fmoney. There are a lot of promotional
OL,13,Factivities taking place in our parks
OL,14,Fwhich the businesses haven't sought
OL,15,Four permission, even though our by-
OL,16,Flaws say that they should.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773087074
OL,3,CSmall businesses say fees to use parks
OL,4,Cand Downs in Bristol are extortionate
OL,6,F"So we don't know whether people are
OL,7,Fqualified to deliver the service that
OL,8,Fthey are to the public. For instance,
OL,9,Fpersonal trainers really should have
OL,10,Fqualifications and we don't know if
OL,11,Fpeople are properly insured in case
OL,12,Fthings go wrong.
OL,14,F"So it's a license for the activity of
OL,15,Fwhich there is a fee. It's not aimed
OL,16,Fat raising lots of money for the
OL,17,Fcouncil."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
